nt-family:宋体;">【收费标准】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学费</span><span style="font-family:;">24000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元（刷卡、现金、支票均可），报名费</span><span style="font-family:;">200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元，教材资料费</span><span style="font-family:;">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">申请学位者参加硕士学位论文指导及答辩等费用，另按北京理工大学相关规定执行；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">注：</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">2012</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">年</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">12</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">月</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">1</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">日前</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">报名学员执行学费</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">20000</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">标准</span></strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【证书颁发】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、学员修完全部课程，并通过结业考试后，经北京理工大学研究生院审核颁发结业证书。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、获得学士学位满三年，已通过所学专业课程的考核与国家组织的全国统一水平考试，并公开发表一篇相关论文，即可以进入硕士学位申请阶段。通过学校论文答辩与学位审批后，可以获得北京理工大学管理学硕士学位。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【特别提醒】</span><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;text-indent:35px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">交学校审核的所有证件材料等须是真实有效的，若因虚假材料造成一切后果由本人承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">申硕说明】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 32px;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">有关申请硕士学位事项按国务院学位委员会</span>[1998]54<span style="font-family:宋体;">号文件的规定和学校的相关规定执行。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">增值服务】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可免费参加北京理工大学管理与经济学院主办的五次高水平讲座；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可加入北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友会，拓宽人脉资源，参加丰富多彩的校友活动。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【联系方式】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名电话：</span>010-68918810&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;010-68918072&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18701396872</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名地点：北京理工大学（东门）管理与经济学院主楼二层</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span>224<span style="font-family:宋体;">室</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">联</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">系</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">钟老师</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">李老师</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-align:center;line-height:29px;"><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1354886664, 0),
(10, '1', '2013年战略管理与产业信息化高级研修班招生简章', '', '', '<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">2013年北京理工大学战略管理与产业信息化高级研修班招生简章</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">（第1期）</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">【前言】</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;在经济全球化的背景下，中国经济快速发展，企业竞争日趋激烈，产业信息化成为大势所趋。信息化时代需要企业高管在复杂环境中掌握产业发展趋势，把控企业发展方向。为了提升信息时代企业高管的战略能力和管理智慧，加强企业高管对产业信息化的掌控能力，北京理工大学管理与经济学院EDP中心专门为企业的董事长、总裁和大型集团公司高层管理人员开设了战略管理与产业信息化课程。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">【学习目标】</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;通过科学务实的课程安排、专业的教学团队和高端的主题论坛提升企业高管战略管理水平和产业信息化掌控能力的同时，建立起产业信息化领域丰厚的高端人脉资源网络。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">【课程特色】</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;设置科学：</span></strong><span style="font-size:16px">课程的设置更科学，更专业，更务实。在学习专业的基础理论知识之外，紧握时代脉搏，设置有战略管理课程和产业信息化课程等实用性综合课程，进一步扩大学员的理论知识领域。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;师资专业：</span></strong><span style="font-size:16px">课程更注重对实际工作能力的培养，由校内具有深厚理论造诣的导师和校外具有丰富实践经验的业内专业人士联袂授课。课程以学习理论知识为主，由北京理工大学专家教授队伍为主要教学力量；同时更注重实践能力，重点强调在工作上的应用，聘请具有丰富实战经验的教授、行业高管、资深专家与学员座谈。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;高端论坛：</span></strong><span style="font-size:16px">在学习课程同时参加定期举办的专业发展讲座及研讨会，协助学员多方面发展专业技能和软性技巧，了解政策、法规和技术快速革新而带来的变化，以增进学员专业知识和管理技能，提升全体学员的素质，在强大竞争中保持独特优势。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;同学联盟：</span></strong><span style="font-size:16px">以知识、人脉、事业为核心，课程学习与校友活动（我校校友分布涉及航天、航空、兵器、银行、证券、房地产、高新技术、投资、贸易等多个行业）同步进行，理论与实践联系更加紧密。学员通过积极参加各项活动，建立高端的人脉资源网络。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">【课程设置】</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;高级研修班课程由战略管理与产业信息化两个模块组成：</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px"></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#555555;font-size:16px">模块一：战略管理课程</span></p><table style="width:388px;border-collapse:collapse" class=" " border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="388" align="center"><colgroup><col style="width:72px" width="72" /><col style="width:316px" width="316" /><tbody><tr style="height:19px" height="19"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:19px" height="19" width="72"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">序号</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">课程</span></td></tr><tr style="height:20px" height="20"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:20px" height="20" width="72"><span style="font-size:16px">1</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">创新管理与企业变革</span></td></tr><tr style="height:20px" height="20"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:20px" height="20" width="72"><span style="font-size:16px">2</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">卓越领导力</span></td></tr><tr style="height:20px" height="20"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:20px" height="20" width="72"><span style="font-size:16px">3</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">企业战略管理</span></td></tr><tr style="height:20px" height="20"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:20px" height="20" width="72"><span style="font-size:16px">4</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">战略人力资源管理</span></td></tr><tr style="height:20px" height="20"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:20px" height="20" width="72"><span style="font-size:16px">5</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">营销管理</span></td></tr><tr style="height:20px" height="20"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:20px" height="20" width="72"><span style="font-size:16px">6</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">企业文化建设与团队沟通</span></td></tr><tr style="height:20px" height="20"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:20px" height="20" width="72"><span style="font-size:16px">7</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">内部成本控制与财力运营管理</span></td></tr><tr style="height:20px" height="20"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:20px" height="20" width="72"><span style="font-size:16px">8</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">投融资分析</span></td></tr><tr style="height:20px" height="20"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:20px" height="20" width="72"><span style="font-size:16px">9</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">公司治理与运营</span></td></tr><tr style="height:20px" height="20"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:20px" height="20" width="72"><span style="font-size:16px">10</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">企业并购与重组</span></td></tr><tr style="height:20px" height="20"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:20px" height="20" width="72"><span style="font-size:16px">11</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">组织行为学</span></td></tr></tbody></colgroup></table><p style="text-align:left;line-height:22px;clear:both;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;"><span style="font-family:&#39;arial&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#555555;font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#555555;font-size:16px">模块二：产业信息化课程</span></p><table style="width:388px;border-collapse:collapse" class=" " border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="388" align="center"><colgroup><col style="width:72px" width="72" /><col style="width:316px" width="316" /><tbody><tr style="height:19px" height="19"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:19px" height="19" width="72"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">序号</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">课程</span></td></tr><tr style="height:20px" height="20"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:20px" height="20" width="72"><span style="font-size:16px">1</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">信息技术战略管理</span></td></tr><tr style="height:20px" height="20"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:20px" height="20" width="72"><span style="font-size:16px">2</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">企业流程重组与企业信息化</span></td></tr><tr style="height:20px" height="20"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:20px" height="20" width="72"><span style="font-size:16px">3</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">供需链管理</span></td></tr><tr style="height:20px" height="20"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:20px" height="20" width="72"><span style="font-size:16px">4</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="color:#555555;font-size:16px">电子政务</span></td></tr><tr style="height:20px" height="20"><td style="background-color:transparent;width:72px;height:20px" height="20" width="72"><span style="font-size:16px">5</span></td><td style="background-color:transparent;width:316px" width="316"><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:16px">IT</span><span style="font-size:16px">项目管理</span></td></tr></tbody></colgroup></table><p style="text-align:left;clear:both">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">【目标学员】</span></p><p>&nbsp;<span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.&nbsp;政府机构、行业主管部门负责信息化建设和信息化项目规划的有关管理人员、实施人员、监理人员；&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．企业负责项目（系统集成项目、软件开发项目、信息系统实施与维护项目等）的高层管理者、项目总监、信息总监、技术总监、项目经理、技术经理、产品经理、部门经理和项目部骨干等人员；&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.&nbsp;各科研机构和高等院校的科研人员、教师及致力于提升自己职业或创业水平的相关人员。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">学&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;制：在职学习一年。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">【课程时间】</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、北京班周末班，每周上课1-2天。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、外地班：学校安排时间进行集中面授；学员在研读期间，学院安排赴北京理工大学访问1-2次（费用自理），学习内容包括专题学术讲座、主题论坛和商务考察等。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">【课程费用】</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;学费38000&nbsp;元（含教材费），进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">【证书取得】</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;通过全部课程及论文考核，获得北京理工大学颁发的结业证书。编入《北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友录》。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">【报名程序】</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、网络报名：进入</span><a style="font-size:18px;text-decoration:underline" href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="font-size:16px">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-size:16px">，“公开课程”模块中“北京理工大学战略管理与产业信息化高级研修班”在线填报，并将最高学历毕业证书复印件发送至edp@bit.edu.cn，经资格审查符合条件者，我院将寄发管理与经济学院“入学通知书”。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、现场报名：北京理工大学主楼219、224房间填写报名表，可当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放“入学通知书”。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">【招生办公室】</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;咨询电话：010—68918810,68918072，68918768</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;招生地点：北京理工大学主楼224室管理与经济学院EDP中心（紧邻地铁魏公村站，位于北京理工大学东门）</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;联系人：&nbsp;李老师&nbsp;&nbsp;钟老师</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1354187786, 0);
INSERT INTO `np_courses` (`id`, `type`, `name`, `photo`, `professor`, `content`, `add_time`, `index`) VALUES
(11, '1', '2012年人力资源总监高级研修班招生简章', '', '', '<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:18px"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">2012年北京理工大学人力资源总监（</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:16px">ＣＨＯ</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:16px">）高级研修班</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:18px"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">招</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:16px"></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:16px">生</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:16px"></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:16px">简</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:16px"></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:16px">章</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">项目背景</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;人力资源总监（CHO）是现代公司中最重要、最有价值的顶尖管理职位之一，是CEO的战略伙伴和核心决策层的重要成员，肩负着制定规划、开发人才、建立机制、管理团队、推动文化等重要职能。推进企业经营管理人才系列化培训，首先必须打造高水平的人力资源总监（CHO）队伍。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">北京理工大学现隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;管理与经济学院的前身是1980年成立的管理工程系，为适应我国社会经济及高等教育发展的需要，1992年，管理工程系更名为管理学院，1998年，更名为管理与经济学院。目前，学院拥有博士生导师27名，副教授及相当职称人员51名，此外，学院还聘请多名政府领导人、中国工程院院士、著名管理经济学专家、企业家为顾问教授、兼职教授。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">北京理工大学人力资源总监（CHO）高级研修班，汇集名校名企一流师资，为人力资源总监、行政主管及其他高层决策人员提供系统的人力资源培训课程</span><em><span style="font-size:16px">、</span></em><span style="font-size:16px">前沿的人力资源理念和最新人力资源管理信息。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;北京理工大学人力资源总监（CHO）高级研修班，以战略为导向建立符合战略需要的人力资源管理体系，为企业人力资源开发与管理提供全面解决方案。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px"></span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">项目特色：</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;借鉴全球人力资源最领先的伦敦经济政治学院专业课程理论，结合中国企业管理的实际，运用本土咨询实操训练的方法，专门针对人力资源总监（CHO）职位自主研发的P-MBA实战管理培训课程。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">1、模块化设置。第一模块：战略为本；第二模块：专业致胜；第三模块：实务立身。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">2、“五位一体”教学法：战略思维修炼&nbsp;+&nbsp;专业知识要领&nbsp;+&nbsp;经典案例剖析&nbsp;+&nbsp;实务模拟&nbsp;+&nbsp;名企考察&nbsp;。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">3、实操结业，权威认证。以完成企业人力资源“选用育留”综合性实务方案为考核学习成果结业，北京理工大学颁发《北京理工大学人力资源总监（CHO）高级研修证书》；并由中国人力资源研究会颁发行业最高标准的《注册高级人力资源管理师》证书，证书钢印备案，编号网站可查。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px"></span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">培训目标</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:16px">：</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;培养具有战略思维、掌握人才开发与管理理论、精通人力资源实务的高层人力资源管理者；特别适合于大型国有企业、上市公司、规模化民营企业的人力资源总监（CHO）。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px"></span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">培训对象要求：</span></strong><span style="font-size:16px">（符合其中一项即可）</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">²&nbsp;企业、事业单位高级人力资源管理者；</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">²&nbsp;本科以上学历且3年以上人力资源管理工作经验；</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">²&nbsp;大专学历且5年以上工作经验，担任人力资源管理工作者。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px"></span><strong><span style="font-size:16px">完成全部培训课程，并考核合格，将获颁如下证书：</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;北京理工大学颁发《北京理工大学人力资源总监（CHO）高级研修证书》；</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">中国人力资源研究会颁发行业最高标准的《注册高级人力资源管理师》证书，证书钢印备</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">案，编号网站可查。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;学员按学校培训管理制度统一管理，建立学员培训档案，同学录加入北京理工大学EDP同学会。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px"></span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">课程体系</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:16px">:&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><table style="border-collapse:collapse" class=" " border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="534" align="center"><tbody><tr><td width="50"><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px">模块</span></strong></p></td><td width="406"><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px">课程名称</span></strong></p></td><td width="39" colspan="2"><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px">学时</span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan="4" width="50"><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px">模块一：</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px">战略为本</span></strong></p></td><td width="406"><p><span style="font-size:16px">《格局、远见、蜕变——人力资源管理者的战略修炼》<br />HR战略转型－战略决定格局<br />HR如何帮助企业远景、使命、核心价值观真正发挥作用？<br />企业三层业务链以及HR如何帮助三层业务链的落地？<br />企业的比较竞争优势以及HR如何帮助企业构建比较竞争优势？<br />企业核心竞争力以及HR如何帮助企业构建核心竞争力？</span></p></td><td width="39" colspan="2"><p><span style="font-size:16px">2天</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="406"><p><span style="font-size:16px">《高管领导力-让员工自愿跟从的能力》<br />如何从管理者跨越到领导者<br />如何获得领导力<br />领导团队的两大秘密<br />高效领导力的“八锅八盖”秘诀（一）<br />高效领导力的“八锅八盖”秘诀（二）</span></p></td><td width="39" colspan="2"><p><span style="font-size:16px">1天</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="406"><p><span style="font-size:16px">《如何打造高效的团队执行力》<br />1、商业人格——打造强大的执行团队<br />2、做结果不做任务－请给我结果<br />3、锡恩４Ｒ运营管理体系——建立不依靠任何能人的制度体系<br />4、中层执行力——中层决定成败</span></p></td><td width="39" colspan="2"><p><span style="font-size:16px">1天</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="406"><p><span style="font-size:16px">《如何打造职业化员工》<br />职业化－让员工从业余选手向职业选手转变<br />专业立身---职业人的生存之本<br />敬业精神---职业人的第二生命<br />职业人的思维训练－“九九归一法”</span></p></td><td width="39" colspan="2"><p><span style="font-size:16px">1天</span></p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan="5" width="50"><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px">模块二：</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px">专业立身</span></strong></p></td><td width="406"><p><span style="font-size:16px">《人力资源角色定义及胜任素质模型》<br />HR胜任素质模型导论<br />Hr&nbsp;角色定义－变革的推动者<br />Hr&nbsp;角色定义－业务伙伴<br />Hr&nbsp;角色定义－领导者角色</span></p></td><td width="39" colspan="2"><p><span style="font-size:16px">1天</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="406"><p><span style="font-size:16px">《战略薪酬管理》<br />薪酬管理如何支撑企业战略的落地<br />全面薪酬管理<br />内部公平性分析&nbsp;<br />外部竞争性分析&nbsp;<br />薪酬结构设计&nbsp;<br />薪酬政策的制定&nbsp;</span></p></td><td width="39" colspan="2"><p><span style="font-size:16px">1天</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="406"><p><span style="font-size:16px">《战略绩效管理》<br />战略绩效管理概述&nbsp;<br />战略如何通过绩效落地<br />如何让绩效管理提高全员的绩效水平<br />评估绩效与员工发展计划&nbsp;</span></p></td><td width="39" colspan="2"><p><span style="font-size:16px">1天</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="406"><p><span style="font-size:16px">《集团管控模式与组织结构设计》<br />组织能力如何保障企业战略的落地<br />企业如何建立强大的组织能力<br />组织运作和人力资源管理的各模块的关系<br />如何设计高效的组织管控模式；<br />如何围绕战略设计公司组织架构；</span></p></td><td width="39" colspan="2"><p><span style="font-size:16px">1天</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="406"><p><span style="font-size:16px">《劳动关系与劳动法》<br />劳动关系概述<br />劳动法律制度<br />劳动合同管理<br />劳动用工制度<br />员工参与管理<br />劳动争议处理</span></p></td><td width="39" colspan="2"><p><span style="font-size:16px">1天</span></p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan="4" width="50"><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px">模块三：</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px">实操为王</span></strong></p></td><td width="406"><p><span style="font-size:16px">《招聘是一场营销》<br />招聘缺少战略导致的三羊现象<br />战略招聘的误区<br />招聘的战略思维<br />招聘是公司文化建立的桥头堡<br />招聘是一场营销－如何吸引战略性人才的进入</span></p></td><td width="39" colspan="2"><p><span style="font-size:16px">1天</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="406"><p><span style="font-size:16px">《录用--建立契约精神》<br />录用如何让员工具有契约精神？<br />录用的流程和工具<br />事前：三合同、一书、一册<br />事中：三合同、一书、一信、三章<br />事后：两书、两单、三图、一笔账</span></p></td><td width="39" colspan="2"><p><span style="font-size:16px">0.5天</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="406"><p><span style="font-size:16px">《培训--把员工成长放在首位》<br />培训的误区<br />建立培训体系比培训本身更重要！<br />建立员工成长的环境和平台<br />如何建立体验式培训<br />如果提高培训的效果</span></p></td><td width="39" colspan="2"><p><span style="font-size:16px">0.5天</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="406"><p><span style="font-size:16px">《专业九段任职资格体系》<br />企业如何通过专业九段体系构建公司的核心能力<br />专业九段的内涵与意义<br />专业九段标准开发的整体流程<br />专业九段与人力资源各模块的对接<br />现有人员的定级实操<br />晋级管理</span></p></td><td width="39" colspan="2"><p><span style="font-size:16px">2天</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="495" colspan="3"><p><span style="font-size:16px">核心课程共三个模块&nbsp;，每月集中上课一次，每次周末连续两天，共计14天，课外交流1天，共计15天</span></p></td><td width="1"><p><span style="font-size:16px"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px"></span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px"></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:16px">授课教师</span></strong><span style="font-size:16px">：（部分授课教师名单：）</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;刘福垣&nbsp;中国人力资源开发研究会会长，研究员、博士导师</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;刘平青&nbsp;北京理工大学管理与经济学院教授，博士生导师，组织与人力资源管理系主任</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;张建卫&nbsp;北京理工大学管理与经济学院副教授，博士生导师，心理学博士</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;王&nbsp;奋&nbsp;北京理工大学管理与经济学院副教授，管理学博士，海底捞顾问</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;孔繁敏&nbsp;北京大学光华管理学院副教授，人力资源和产业关系学博士</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;王&nbsp;辉&nbsp;北京大学光华管理学院组织管理系教授，博士生导师，系主任，组织管理学博士</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;梁钧平&nbsp;北京大学光华管理学院教授，博士生导师，著名企业人力资源管理专家</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;王&nbsp;垒&nbsp;北京大学心理学系教授心理学博士，国家人事部人力资源管理专业经济师考试专家组专家</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;张智勇&nbsp;北京大学副教授，北京社会心理学会理事、副秘书长</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;吕&nbsp;锋&nbsp;北京大学光华管理学院人力资源管理专业博士后，北京大学光华管理学院校友联络中心主任</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;余顺坤&nbsp;华北电力大学教授，北京地区高校人力资源协会会长</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;姜汝祥&nbsp;北京大学博士，战略人力资源管理专家，锡恩企业管理咨询公司董事长</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;杨鹏博&nbsp;北京锡恩英才人力资源管理顾问公司副总经理、高级培训师</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;邢&nbsp;涛&nbsp;北京锡恩英才人力资源管理顾问公司培训中心总经理、高级培训师</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;李&nbsp;彬&nbsp;北京锡恩英才人力资源管理顾问公司顾问中心总经理、高级培训师</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;马永强&nbsp;北京锡恩英才人力资源管理顾问公司高级培训师</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;曹际鹏&nbsp;锡恩公司原副总裁、华益维新咨询公司总裁，战略人力资源专家</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">☆&nbsp;沈小滨&nbsp;锡恩公司原副总裁、知行韬略咨询公司总经理，战略人力资源专家</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px"></span></p><p style="text-align:left"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">关于研修的安排</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">学&nbsp;费：人民币36000元/人（含学费、教材费、证书；交通、食宿费用自理）；</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">汇入如下北京理工大学账户：</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">开户名称：&nbsp;北京理工大学<br />开户银行：中国工商银行北京紫竹院支行</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">银行帐号：0200007609014435495</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">汇款附言请注明：&nbsp;管理与经济学院XX（学员姓名）CHO培训费</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">学&nbsp;制：15天的课程，每月集中一个周末到北京理工大学学习2天，常年循环举办，缺课可补；</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">名&nbsp;额：限40人，额满为止；</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">培训地点：北京理工大学。</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">报名电话：010-68918810&nbsp;传真：&nbsp;010-68918072</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">报名地点：北京理工大学主楼219室EDP中心<br />网址：http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></p><p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:16px">地址：&nbsp;北京市海淀区中关村南大街5号</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p></p>', 1354188018, 0),
(35, '2', '2013年工商管理专业（创新管理与可持续发展方向）在职研究生课程进修班', '', '', '<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/13548865545987.png" /><img style="width:267px;height:54px;" title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/13548865547779.jpg" width="280" height="73" />&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班工商管理专业</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">（</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">创新管理与可持续发展</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">方向）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:19px;">（可申请管理学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，对接企业对项目管理人才职业资格的需要，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办工商管理专业（<span style="color:black;">创新管理与可持续发展方向</span>）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">3<span style="font-family:宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">招生人数：</span>60<span style="font-family:宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-family:calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family:;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family:;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-indent:14px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中国特色社会主义理论与实践研究</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">自然辩证法概论</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="5" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">现代管理理论与方法</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">战略管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">市场营销管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">财务管理理论与方法</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">宏观经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">人力资源管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">技术创新管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">品牌管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin:15px 0cm 0px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">管理沟通</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">企业经营决策模拟</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">员工关系管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">企业并购与公司治理</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent:54px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 36px;border:currentcolor;width:501px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm 7px;border:1px solid black;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">次</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">报名及注册时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">开课时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1341</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2012</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1342</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1343</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1344</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">10</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">16</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【收费标准】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学费</span><span style="font-family:;">24000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元（刷卡、现金、支票均可），报名费</span><span style="font-family:;">200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元，教材资料费</span><span style="font-family:;">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">申请学位者参加硕士学位论文指导及答辩等费用，另按北京理工大学相关规定执行；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">注：</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">2012</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">年</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">12</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">月</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">1</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">日前</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">报名学员执行学费</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">20000</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">标准</span></strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【证书颁发】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、学员修完全部课程，并通过结业考试后，经北京理工大学研究生院审核颁发结业证书。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、获得学士学位满三年，已通过所学专业课程的考核与国家组织的全国统一水平考试，并公开发表一篇相关论文，即可以进入硕士学位申请阶段。通过学校论文答辩与学位审批后，可以获得北京理工大学管理学硕士学位。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【特别提醒】</span><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;text-indent:35px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">交学校审核的所有证件材料等须是真实有效的，若因虚假材料造成一切后果由本人承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">申硕说明】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 32px;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">有关申请硕士学位事项按国务院学位委员会</span>[1998]54<span style="font-family:宋体;">号文件的规定和学校的相关规定执行。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">增值服务】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可免费参加北京理工大学管理与经济学院主办的五次高水平讲座；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可加入北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友会，拓宽人脉资源，参加丰富多彩的校友活动。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【联系方式】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名电话：</span>010-68918810&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;010-68918072&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18701396872</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名地点：北京理工大学（东门）管理与经济学院主楼二层</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span>224<span style="font-family:宋体;">室</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">联</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">系</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">钟老师</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">李老师</span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1354886597, 0);
INSERT INTO `np_courses` (`id`, `type`, `name`, `photo`, `professor`, `content`, `add_time`, `index`) VALUES
(34, '2', '2013年工商管理专业（项目管理方向）在职研究生课程进修班', '', '', '<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/13548864883519.png" /><img style="width:240px;height:59px;" title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/1354886488760.jpg" width="310" height="77" />&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班工商管理专业</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">（项目管理方向）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:19px;">（可申请管理学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，对接企业对项目管理人才职业资格的需要，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办工商管理专业（项目管理方向）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">3<span style="font-family:宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">招生人数：</span>60<span style="font-family:宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-family:calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family:;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family:;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-indent:14px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中国特色社会主义理论与实践研究</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">自然辩证法概论</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="5" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">现代管理理论与方法</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">战略管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">市场营销管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">财务管理理论与方法</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">宏观经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">人力资源管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">技术创新管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">品牌管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin:15px 0cm 0px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">项目管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">管理沟通</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">员工关系管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">渠道管理</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent:54px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 36px;border:currentcolor;width:501px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm 7px;border:1px solid black;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">次</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">报名及注册时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">开课时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1351</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2012</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1352</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1353</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1354</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">10</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">16</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【收费标准】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学费</span><span style="font-family:;">24000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元（刷卡、现金、支票均可），报名费</span><span style="font-family:;">200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元，教材资料费</span><span style="font-family:;">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">申请学位者参加硕士学位论文指导及答辩等费用，另按北京理工大学相关规定执行；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">注：</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">2012</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">年</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">12</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">月</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">1</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">日前</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">报名学员执行学费</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">20000</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">标准</span></strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【证书颁发】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、学员修完全部课程，并通过结业考试后，经北京理工大学研究生院审核颁发结业证书。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、获得学士学位满三年，已通过所学专业课程的考核与国家组织的全国统一水平考试，并公开发表一篇相关论文，即可以进入硕士学位申请阶段。通过学校论文答辩与学位审批后，可以获得北京理工大学管理学硕士学位。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【特别提醒】</span><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;text-indent:35px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">交学校审核的所有证件材料等须是真实有效的，若因虚假材料造成一切后果由本人承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">申硕说明】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 32px;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">有关申请硕士学位事项按国务院学位委员会</span>[1998]54<span style="font-family:宋体;">号文件的规定和学校的相关规定执行。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">增值服务】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可免费参加北京理工大学管理与经济学院主办的五次高水平讲座；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可加入北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友会，拓宽人脉资源，参加丰富多彩的校友活动。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【联系方式】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名电话：</span>010-68918810&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;010-68918072&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18701396872</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名地点：北京理工大学（东门）管理与经济学院主楼二层</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span>224<span style="font-family:宋体;">室</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">联</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">系</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">钟老师</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">李老师</span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1354886530, 0);
INSERT INTO `np_courses` (`id`, `type`, `name`, `photo`, `professor`, `content`, `add_time`, `index`) VALUES
(33, '2', '2013年工商管理专业（技术创新与科技评价方向）在职研究生课程进修班', '', '', '<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/13548864228607.png" /><img style="width:301px;height:60px;" title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/13548864227821.jpg" width="307" height="61" />&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班工商管理专业</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">（技术创新与科技评价方向）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:19px;">（可申请管理学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，对接企业对技术人才与管理人才职业资格的需要，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办工商管理专业（技术创新与科技评价方向）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">3<span style="font-family:宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">招生人数：</span>60<span style="font-family:宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-family:calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family:;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family:;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-indent:14px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中国特色社会主义理论与实践研究</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">自然辩证法概论</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="5" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">现代管理理论与方法</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">战略管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">市场营销管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">财务管理理论与方法</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">宏观经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">人力资源管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">技术创新管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">品牌管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin:15px 0cm 0px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">品牌管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">管理沟通</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">项目管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">员工关系管理</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent:54px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 75px;border:currentcolor;width:501px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm 7px;border:1px solid black;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">次</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">报名及注册时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">开课时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1361</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2012</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1362</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1363</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1364</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">10</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">16</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【收费标准】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学费</span><span style="font-family:;">24000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元（刷卡、现金、支票均可），报名费</span><span style="font-family:;">200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元，教材资料费</span><span style="font-family:;">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">申请学位者参加硕士学位论文指导及答辩等费用，另按北京理工大学相关规定执行；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">注：</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">2012</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">年</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">12</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">月</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">1</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">日前</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">报名学员执行学费</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">20000</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">标准</span></strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【证书颁发】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、学员修完全部课程，并通过结业考试后，经北京理工大学研究生院审核颁发结业证书。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、获得学士学位满三年，已通过所学专业课程的考核与国家组织的全国统一水平考试，并公开发表一篇相关论文，即可以进入硕士学位申请阶段。通过学校论文答辩与学位审批后，可以获得北京理工大学管理学硕士学位。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【特别提醒】</span><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;text-indent:35px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">交学校审核的所有证件材料等须是真实有效的，若因虚假材料造成一切后果由本人承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">申硕说明】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 32px;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">有关申请硕士学位事项按国务院学位委员会</span>[1998]54<span style="font-family:宋体;">号文件的规定和学校的相关规定执行。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">增值服务】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可免费参加北京理工大学管理与经济学院主办的五次高水平讲座；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可加入北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友会，拓宽人脉资源，参加丰富多彩的校友活动。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【联系方式】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名电话：</span>010-68918810&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;010-68918072&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18701396872</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名地点：北京理工大学（东门）管理与经济学院主楼二层</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span>224<span style="font-family:宋体;">室</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">联</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">系</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">钟老师</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">李老师</span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1354886461, 0);
INSERT INTO `np_courses` (`id`, `type`, `name`, `photo`, `professor`, `content`, `add_time`, `index`) VALUES
(32, '2', '2013年工商管理专业（投融资与风险管理方向）在职研究生课程进修班', '', '', '<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/13548863374733.png" /><img style="width:300px;height:63px;" title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/13548863371503.jpg" width="300" height="59" />&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班工商管理专业</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">（</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">投融资与风险管理</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">方向）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:19px;">（可申请管理学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，对接企业对项目管理人才职业资格的需要，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办工商管理专业（<span style="color:black;">投融资与风险管理方向</span>）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">3<span style="font-family:宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">招生人数：</span>60<span style="font-family:宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-family:calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family:;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family:;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-indent:14px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中国特色社会主义理论与实践研究</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">自然辩证法概论</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="5" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">现代管理理论与方法</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">战略管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">市场营销管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">财务管理理论与方法</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">宏观经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">审计理论与方法</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">技术创新管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">品牌管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin:15px 0cm 0px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">管理沟通</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">企业经营决策模拟</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">员工关系管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">企业并购与公司治理</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent:54px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 36px;border:currentcolor;width:501px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm 7px;border:1px solid black;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">次</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">报名及注册时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">开课时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1341</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2012</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1342</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1343</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1344</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">10</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">16</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【收费标准】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学费</span><span style="font-family:;">24000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元（刷卡、现金、支票均可），报名费</span><span style="font-family:;">200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元，教材资料费</span><span style="font-family:;">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">申请学位者参加硕士学位论文指导及答辩等费用，另按北京理工大学相关规定执行；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">注：</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">2012</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">年</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">12</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">月</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">1</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">日前</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">报名学员执行学费</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">20000</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">标准</span></strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【证书颁发】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、学员修完全部课程，并通过结业考试后，经北京理工大学研究生院审核颁发结业证书。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、获得学士学位满三年，已通过所学专业课程的考核与国家组织的全国统一水平考试，并公开发表一篇相关论文，即可以进入硕士学位申请阶段。通过学校论文答辩与学位审批后，可以获得北京理工大学管理学硕士学位。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【特别提醒】</span><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;text-indent:35px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">交学校审核的所有证件材料等须是真实有效的，若因虚假材料造成一切后果由本人承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">申硕说明】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 32px;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">有关申请硕士学位事项按国务院学位委员会</span>[1998]54<span style="font-family:宋体;">号文件的规定和学校的相关规定执行。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">增值服务】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可免费参加北京理工大学管理与经济学院主办的五次高水平讲座；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可加入北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友会，拓宽人脉资源，参加丰富多彩的校友活动。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【联系方式】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名电话：</span>010-68918810&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;010-68918072&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18701396872</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名地点：北京理工大学（东门）管理与经济学院主楼二层</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span>224<span style="font-family:宋体;">室</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">联</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">系</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">钟老师</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">李老师</span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1354886386, 0),
(31, '2', '2013年管理科学与工程专业（现代管理与决策理论方向）在职研究生课程进修班', '', '', '<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/13548862487683.png" /></span></strong><strong><span style="color:blue;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/13548862499095.jpg" width="281" height="60" />&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#333300;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班管理科学与工程专业</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:21px;">（</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:21px;">现代管理与决策理论</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:21px;">方向）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;font-size:19px;">（可申请管理学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办管理科学与工程专业（</span><span style="color:black;font-family:宋体;">现代管理与决策理论</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">方向）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">3<span style="font-family:宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-family:calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">招生人数：</span>30<span style="font-family:宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family:;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family:;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-indent:14px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科学社会主义理论与实践研究</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科学技术哲学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="3" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">决策方法导论</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">物流与供应链管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">信息系统工程</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">运筹学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">高等概率与数理统计</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin:15px 0cm 0px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">管理对策论</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">物联网与云计算</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">离散信息仿真</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent:54px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><div align="center"><table style="margin:auto auto auto 36px;border:currentcolor;width:501px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm 7px;border:1px solid black;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">次</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">报名时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">开课时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">12010011</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2012</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">12010012</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【收费标准】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学费</span><span style="font-family:;">20000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元（刷卡、现金、支票均可），报名费</span><span style="font-family:;">200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元，教材资料费</span><span style="font-family:;">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">申请学位者参加硕士学位论文指导及答辩等费用，另按北京理工大学相关规定执行；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【证书颁发】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、学员修完全部课程，并通过结业考试后，经北京理工大学研究生院审核颁发结业证书。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、获得学士学位满三年，已通过所学专业课程的考核与国家组织的全国统一水平考试，并公开发表一篇相关论文，即可以进入硕士学位申请阶段。通过学校论文答辩与学位审批后，可以获得北京理工大学管理学硕士学位。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【特别提醒】</span><span style="color:#003300;"></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;text-indent:35px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">交学校审核的所有证件材料等须是真实有效的，若因虚假材料造成一切后果由本人承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">申硕说明】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 32px;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">有关申请硕士学位事项按国务院学位委员会</span>[1998]54<span style="font-family:宋体;">号文件的规定和学校的相关规定执行。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">增值服务】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可免费参加北京理工大学管理与经济学院主办的五次高水平讲座；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可加入北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友会，拓宽人脉资源，参加丰富多彩的校友活动。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【联系方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名电话：</span>010-68918810&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;010-68918072&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18701396872</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名地点：北京理工大学（东门）管理与经济学院<span style="color:black;">主楼二层</span></span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span>224<span style="font-family:宋体;">室</span><span style="font-family:calibri;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">联</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">系</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">钟老师</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">李老师</span></span></p><p style="line-height:27px;"><span style="font-family:;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1354886299, 0);
INSERT INTO `np_courses` (`id`, `type`, `name`, `photo`, `professor`, `content`, `add_time`, `index`) VALUES
(29, '2', '2013年管理科学与工程专业（知识管理与创新管理方向）在职研究生课程进修班', '', '', '<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/1354886043100.png" /></span></strong><strong><span style="color:blue;font-family:;"><img style="width:255px;height:51px;" title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/13548860434708.jpg" width="248" height="46" />&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#333300;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班管理科学与工程专业</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:21px;">（</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:21px;">知识管理与创新管理方向</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:21px;">）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;font-size:19px;">（可申请管理学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办管理科学与工程专业（</span><span style="color:black;font-family:宋体;">知识管理与创新管理方向</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">3<span style="font-family:宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-family:calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">招生人数：</span>30<span style="font-family:宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family:;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family:;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-indent:14px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科学社会主义理论与实践</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科学技术哲学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="3" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">管理系统工程</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">决策方法导论</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">信息系统工程</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">工业工程理论与方法</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">高等概率与数理统计</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin:15px 0cm 0px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">知识管理与创新管理理论方法</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">知识产权战略</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">管理对策论</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent:54px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><div align="center"><table style="margin:auto auto auto 36px;border:currentcolor;width:501px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm 7px;border:1px solid black;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">次</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">报名时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">开课时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">12010051</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2012</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">12010052</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【收费标准】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学费</span><span style="font-family:;">20000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元（刷卡、现金、支票均可），报名费</span><span style="font-family:;">200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元，教材资料费</span><span style="font-family:;">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">申请学位者参加硕士学位论文指导及答辩等费用，另按北京理工大学相关规定执行；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【证书颁发】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、学员修完全部课程，并通过结业考试后，经北京理工大学研究生院审核颁发结业证书。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、获得学士学位满三年，已通过所学专业课程的考核与国家组织的全国统一水平考试，并公开发表一篇相关论文，即可以进入硕士学位申请阶段。通过学校论文答辩与学位审批后，可以获得北京理工大学管理学硕士学位。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【特别提醒】</span><span style="color:#003300;"></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;text-indent:35px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">交学校审核的所有证件材料等须是真实有效的，若因虚假材料造成一切后果由本人承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">申硕说明】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 32px;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">有关申请硕士学位事项按国务院学位委员会</span>[1998]54<span style="font-family:宋体;">号文件的规定和学校的相关规定执行。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">增值服务】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可免费参加北京理工大学管理与经济学院主办的五次高水平讲座；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可加入北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友会，拓宽人脉资源，参加丰富多彩的校友活动。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【联系方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名电话：</span>010-68918810&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;010-68918072&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18701396872</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名地点：北京理工大学（东门）管理与经济学院<span style="color:black;">主楼二层</span></span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span>224<span style="font-family:宋体;">室</span><span style="font-family:calibri;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">联</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">系</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">钟老师</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">李老师</span></span></p><p style="line-height:27px;"><span style="font-family:;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1354886103, 0),
(30, '2', '2013年管理科学与工程专业（风险管理方向）在职研究生课程进修班', '', '', '<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/13548861652340.png" /></span></strong><strong><span style="color:blue;font-family:;"><img style="width:274px;height:58px;" title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/13548861659585.jpg" width="288" height="65" />&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#333300;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班管理科学与工程专业</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:21px;">（</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:21px;">风险管理方向</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:21px;">）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;font-size:19px;">（可申请管理学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办管理科学与工程专业（</span><span style="color:black;font-family:宋体;">风险管理方向</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">3<span style="font-family:宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-family:calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">招生人数：</span>30<span style="font-family:宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family:;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family:;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-indent:14px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科学社会主义理论与实践</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科学技术哲学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="3" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">信息系统工程</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">决策方法导论</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">网络信息内容安全</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">运筹学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">高等概率与数理统计</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin:15px 0cm 0px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">定量风险管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">物联网与云计算</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">可靠性工程</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent:54px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><div align="center"><table style="margin:auto auto auto 36px;border:currentcolor;width:501px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm 7px;border:1px solid black;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">次</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">报名时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">开课时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">12010031</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2012</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">12010032</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【收费标准】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学费</span><span style="font-family:;">20000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元（刷卡、现金、支票均可），报名费</span><span style="font-family:;">200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元，教材资料费</span><span style="font-family:;">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">申请学位者参加硕士学位论文指导及答辩等费用，另按北京理工大学相关规定执行；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【证书颁发】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、学员修完全部课程，并通过结业考试后，经北京理工大学研究生院审核颁发结业证书。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、获得学士学位满三年，已通过所学专业课程的考核与国家组织的全国统一水平考试，并公开发表一篇相关论文，即可以进入硕士学位申请阶段。通过学校论文答辩与学位审批后，可以获得北京理工大学管理学硕士学位。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【特别提醒】</span><span style="color:#003300;"></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;text-indent:35px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">交学校审核的所有证件材料等须是真实有效的，若因虚假材料造成一切后果由本人承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">申硕说明】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 32px;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">有关申请硕士学位事项按国务院学位委员会</span>[1998]54<span style="font-family:宋体;">号文件的规定和学校的相关规定执行。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">增值服务】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可免费参加北京理工大学管理与经济学院主办的五次高水平讲座；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可加入北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友会，拓宽人脉资源，参加丰富多彩的校友活动。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【联系方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名电话：</span>010-68918810&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;010-68918072&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18701396872</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名地点：北京理工大学（东门）管理与经济学院<span style="color:black;">主楼二层</span></span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span>224<span style="font-family:宋体;">室</span><span style="font-family:calibri;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">联</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">系</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">钟老师</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">李老师</span></span></p><p style="line-height:27px;"><span style="font-family:;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1354886218, 0);
INSERT INTO `np_courses` (`id`, `type`, `name`, `photo`, `professor`, `content`, `add_time`, `index`) VALUES
(28, '2', '2013年管理科学与工程专业（复杂系统建模与管理系统工程方向）在职研究生课程进修班', '', '', '<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/13548859611125.png" /></span></strong><strong><span style="color:blue;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/13548859617942.jpg" width="271" height="60" />&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#333300;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班管理科学与工程专业</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:21px;">（</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:21px;">复杂系统建模与管理系统工程方向</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:21px;">）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;font-size:19px;">（可申请管理学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办管理科学与工程专业（</span><span style="color:black;font-family:宋体;">复杂系统建模与管理系统工程方向</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">3<span style="font-family:宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-family:calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">招生人数：</span>30<span style="font-family:宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family:;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family:;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-indent:14px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科学社会主义理论与实践</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科学技术哲学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="3" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">管理系统工程</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">决策方法导论</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">信息系统工程</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">工业工程理论与方法</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">高等概率与数理统计</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin:15px 0cm 0px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">管理对策论</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">离散系统仿真</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">可靠性工程</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent:54px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><div align="center"><table style="margin:auto auto auto 36px;border:currentcolor;width:501px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm 7px;border:1px solid black;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">次</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">报名时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">开课时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">12010041</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2012</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">12010042</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【收费标准】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学费</span><span style="font-family:;">20000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元（刷卡、现金、支票均可），报名费</span><span style="font-family:;">200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元，教材资料费</span><span style="font-family:;">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">申请学位者参加硕士学位论文指导及答辩等费用，另按北京理工大学相关规定执行；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【证书颁发】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、学员修完全部课程，并通过结业考试后，经北京理工大学研究生院审核颁发结业证书。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、获得学士学位满三年，已通过所学专业课程的考核与国家组织的全国统一水平考试，并公开发表一篇相关论文，即可以进入硕士学位申请阶段。通过学校论文答辩与学位审批后，可以获得北京理工大学管理学硕士学位。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【特别提醒】</span><span style="color:#003300;"></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;text-indent:35px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">交学校审核的所有证件材料等须是真实有效的，若因虚假材料造成一切后果由本人承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">申硕说明】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 32px;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">有关申请硕士学位事项按国务院学位委员会</span>[1998]54<span style="font-family:宋体;">号文件的规定和学校的相关规定执行。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">增值服务】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可免费参加北京理工大学管理与经济学院主办的五次高水平讲座；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可加入北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友会，拓宽人脉资源，参加丰富多彩的校友活动。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【联系方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名电话：</span>010-68918810&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;010-68918072&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18701396872</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名地点：北京理工大学（东门）管理与经济学院<span style="color:black;">主楼二层</span></span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span>224<span style="font-family:宋体;">室</span><span style="font-family:calibri;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">联</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">系</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">钟老师</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">李老师</span></span></p><p style="line-height:27px;"><span style="font-family:;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1354886016, 0),
(27, '2', '2013年管理科学与工程专业（信息管理与信息系统方向）在职研究生课程进修班', '', '', '<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/13548858497266.png" /></span></strong><strong><span style="color:blue;font-family:;"><img style="width:261px;height:60px;" title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/13548858495721.jpg" width="270" height="64" />&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#333300;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班管理科学与工程专业</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">（</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">信息管理与信息系统方向</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;font-size:19px;">（可申请管理学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办管理科学与工程专业（</span><span style="color:black;font-family:宋体;">信息管理与信息系统方向</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">3<span style="font-family:宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-family:calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">招生人数：</span>30<span style="font-family:宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family:;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family:;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-indent:14px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中国特色社会主义理论与实践研究</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科学技术哲学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="3" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">信息系统工程</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">决策方法导论</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">网络信息内容安全</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">运筹学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">高等概率与数理统计</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin:15px 0cm 0px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">管理对策论</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">物联网与云计算</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">离散信息仿真</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent:54px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><div align="center"><table style="margin:auto auto auto 36px;border:currentcolor;width:501px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm 7px;border:1px solid black;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">次</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">报名时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">开课时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">12010021</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2012</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">12010022</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【收费标准】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学费</span><span style="font-family:;">20000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元（刷卡、现金、支票均可），报名费</span><span style="font-family:;">200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元，教材资料费</span><span style="font-family:;">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">申请学位者参加硕士学位论文指导及答辩等费用，另按北京理工大学相关规定执行；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【证书颁发】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、学员修完全部课程，并通过结业考试后，经北京理工大学研究生院审核颁发结业证书。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、获得学士学位满三年，已通过所学专业课程的考核与国家组织的全国统一水平考试，并公开发表一篇相关论文，即可以进入硕士学位申请阶段。通过学校论文答辩与学位审批后，可以获得北京理工大学管理学硕士学位。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【特别提醒】</span><span style="color:#003300;"></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;text-indent:35px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">交学校审核的所有证件材料等须是真实有效的，若因虚假材料造成一切后果由本人承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">申硕说明】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 32px;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">有关申请硕士学位事项按国务院学位委员会</span>[1998]54<span style="font-family:宋体;">号文件的规定和学校的相关规定执行。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">增值服务】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可免费参加北京理工大学管理与经济学院主办的五次高水平讲座；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可加入北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友会，拓宽人脉资源，参加丰富多彩的校友活动。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#003300;font-family:宋体;">【联系方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#003300;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名电话：</span>010-68918810&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;010-68918072&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18701396872</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名地点：北京理工大学（东门）管理与经济学院<span style="color:black;">主楼二层</span></span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span>224<span style="font-family:宋体;">室</span><span style="font-family:calibri;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">联</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">系</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">钟老师</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">李老师</span></span></p><p style="line-height:27px;"><span style="font-family:;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1354885921, 0);
INSERT INTO `np_courses` (`id`, `type`, `name`, `photo`, `professor`, `content`, `add_time`, `index`) VALUES
(26, '2', '2013年应用经济学专业（金融学方向）在职研究生课程进修班', '', '', '<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/13548853451770.png" /></span></strong><strong><span style="color:blue;font-family:;"><img style="width:290px;height:52px;" title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/13548853468196.jpg" width="335" height="66" />&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#333300;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班应用经济学专业</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">（金融学方向）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:green;font-family:宋体;font-size:19px;">（可申请经济学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color:green;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，对接企业对人力资源工作岗位职业资格的需要，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办应用经济学专业（金融学方向）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">3<span style="font-family:宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-family:calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">招生人数：</span>30<span style="font-family:宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family:;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family:;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-indent:14px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" class=" " border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中国特色社会主义理论与实践研究</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科学技术哲学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="3" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">金融经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">金融市场学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">国际投资学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级计量经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级宏观经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin:15px 0cm 0px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">金融投资分析</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">国际贸易实务</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">现代商务策划与管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent:54px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><div align="center"><table style="margin:auto auto auto 36px;border:currentcolor;width:501px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm 7px;border:1px solid black;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">次</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">报名时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">开课时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">02020031</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2012</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">02020032</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【收费标准】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学费</span><span style="font-family:;">20000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元（刷卡、现金、支票均可），报名费</span><span style="font-family:;">200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元，教材资料费</span><span style="font-family:;">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">申请学位者参加硕士学位论文指导及答辩等费用，另按北京理工大学相关规定执行；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【证书颁发】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、学员修完全部课程，并通过结业考试后，经北京理工大学研究生院审核颁发结业证书。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、获得学士学位满三年，已通过所学专业课程的考核与国家组织的全国统一水平考试，并公开发表一篇相关论文，即可以进入硕士学位申请阶段。通过学校论文答辩与学位审批后，可以获得北京理工大学管理学硕士学位。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【特别提醒】</span><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;text-indent:35px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">交学校审核的所有证件材料等须是真实有效的，若因虚假材料造成一切后果由本人承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">申硕说明】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 32px;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">有关申请硕士学位事项按国务院学位委员会</span>[1998]54<span style="font-family:宋体;">号文件的规定和学校的相关规定执行。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">增值服务】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可免费参加北京理工大学管理与经济学院主办的五次高水平讲座；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可加入北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友会，拓宽人脉资源，参加丰富多彩的校友活动。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【联系方式】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名电话：</span>010-68918810&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;010-68918072&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18701396872</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名地点：北京理工大学（东门）管理与经济学院<span style="color:black;">主楼二层</span></span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span>224<span style="font-family:宋体;">室</span><span style="font-family:calibri;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">联</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">系</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">钟老师</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">李老师</span></span></p><p style="line-height:27px;"><span style="font-family:;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1354885411, 0),
(25, '2', '2013年应用经济学专业（国际贸易方向）在职研究生课程进修班', '', '', '<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/13548851946678.png" /></span></strong><strong><span style="color:blue;font-family:;"><img style="width:267px;height:56px;" title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/13548851942551.jpg" width="326" height="74" />&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#333300;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班应用经济学专业</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">（国际贸易方向）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:green;font-family:宋体;font-size:19px;">（可申请经济学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color:green;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，对接企业对人力资源工作岗位职业资格的需要，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办应用经济学专业（国际贸易方向）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">3<span style="font-family:宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-family:calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">招生人数：</span>30<span style="font-family:宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family:;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family:;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-indent:14px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" class=" " border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中国特色社会主义理论与实践研究</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科学技术哲学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="3" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">金融经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">国际贸易理论与政策</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">国际投资学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级计量经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级宏观经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin:15px 0cm 0px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">国际贸易实务</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">国际贸易结算</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">现代商务策划与管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent:54px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><div align="center"><table style="margin:auto auto auto 36px;border:currentcolor;width:501px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm 7px;border:1px solid black;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">次</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">报名时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">开课时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">02020021</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2012</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">02020022</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【收费标准】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学费</span><span style="font-family:;">22000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元（刷卡、现金、支票均可），报名费</span><span style="font-family:;">200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元，教材资料费</span><span style="font-family:;">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">申请学位者参加硕士学位论文指导及答辩等费用，另按北京理工大学相关规定执行；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【证书颁发】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、学员修完全部课程，并通过结业考试后，经北京理工大学研究生院审核颁发结业证书。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、获得学士学位满三年，已通过所学专业课程的考核与国家组织的全国统一水平考试，并公开发表一篇相关论文，即可以进入硕士学位申请阶段。通过学校论文答辩与学位审批后，可以获得北京理工大学管理学硕士学位。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【特别提醒】</span><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;text-indent:35px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">交学校审核的所有证件材料等须是真实有效的，若因虚假材料造成一切后果由本人承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">申硕说明】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 32px;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">有关申请硕士学位事项按国务院学位委员会</span>[1998]54<span style="font-family:宋体;">号文件的规定和学校的相关规定执行。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">增值服务】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可免费参加北京理工大学管理与经济学院主办的五次高水平讲座；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可加入北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友会，拓宽人脉资源，参加丰富多彩的校友活动。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【联系方式】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名电话：</span>010-68918810&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;010-68918072&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18701396872</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名地点：北京理工大学（东门）管理与经济学院<span style="color:black;">主楼二层</span></span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span>224<span style="font-family:宋体;">室</span><span style="font-family:calibri;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">联</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">系</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">钟老师</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">李老师</span></span></p><p style="line-height:27px;"><span style="font-family:;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1354885295, 0);
INSERT INTO `np_courses` (`id`, `type`, `name`, `photo`, `professor`, `content`, `add_time`, `index`) VALUES
(23, '2', '2013年应用经济学专业（国防经济学方向）在职研究生课程进修班', '', '', '<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"><img style="float:none;" title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/13548843587629.png" /></span></strong><img style="width:248px;height:55px;" title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/13548843587352.jpg" width="359" height="86" /></p><p style="text-align:left;"><strong><span style="color:blue;font-family:;">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#333300;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班应用经济学专业</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">（国防经济学方向）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:green;font-family:宋体;font-size:19px;">（可申请经济学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color:green;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:left;text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-align:left;text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，对接企业对人力资源工作岗位职业资格的需要，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办应用经济学专业（国防经济学方向）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align:left;text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员；</span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位；</span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">3<span style="font-family:宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-family:calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">招生人数：</span>30<span style="font-family:宋体;">人</span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align:left;text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family:;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family:;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-align:left;text-indent:14px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align:left;text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:left;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:left;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:left;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中国特色社会主义理论与实践研究</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科学技术哲学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="3" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:left;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">国防经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">金融经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">国际投资学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级计量经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级宏观经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin:15px 0cm 0px;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">国防经济运行与管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">高级国防经济分析</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">现代商务策划与管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-align:left;text-indent:54px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><div style="text-align:left;" align="center"><table style="margin:auto auto auto 36px;border:currentcolor;width:501px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm 7px;border:1px solid black;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:left;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">次</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:left;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">报名时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:left;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">开课时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:;">02020041</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:;">2012</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:;">02020042</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【收费标准】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学费</span><span style="font-family:;">20000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元（刷卡、现金、支票均可），报名费</span><span style="font-family:;">200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元，教材资料费</span><span style="font-family:;">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">申请学位者参加硕士学位论文指导及答辩等费用，另按北京理工大学相关规定执行；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【证书颁发】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align:left;text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、学员修完全部课程，并通过结业考试后，经北京理工大学研究生院审核颁发结业证书。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、获得学士学位满三年，已通过所学专业课程的考核与国家组织的全国统一水平考试，并公开发表一篇相关论文，即可以进入硕士学位申请阶段。通过学校论文答辩与学位审批后，可以获得北京理工大学管理学硕士学位。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;"><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【特别提醒】</span><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;text-indent:35px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">交学校审核的所有证件材料等须是真实有效的，若因虚假材料造成一切后果由本人承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">申硕说明】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 32px;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">有关申请硕士学位事项按国务院学位委员会</span>[1998]54<span style="font-family:宋体;">号文件的规定和学校的相关规定执行。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">增值服务】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可免费参加北京理工大学管理与经济学院主办的五次高水平讲座；</span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可加入北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友会，拓宽人脉资源，参加丰富多彩的校友活动。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【联系方式】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名电话：</span>010-68918810&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;010-68918072&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18701396872</span></p><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名地点：北京理工大学（东门）管理与经济学院<span style="color:black;">主楼二层</span></span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span>224<span style="font-family:宋体;">室</span><span style="font-family:calibri;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">联</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">系</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">钟老师</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">李老师</span></span></p><p style="line-height:27px;"><span style="font-family:;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>', 1354884406, 0),
(24, '2', '2013年应用经济学专业（产业经济学方向）年在职研究生课程进修班', '', '', '<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/13548850526837.png" /></span></strong><strong><span style="color:blue;font-family:;"><img style="width:240px;height:53px;" title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/13548850536678.jpg" width="382" height="84" />&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#333300;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班应用经济学专业</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">（产业经济学方向）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:green;font-family:宋体;font-size:19px;">（可申请经济学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color:green;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，对接企业对人力资源工作岗位职业资格的需要，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办应用经济学专业（产业经济学方向）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">3<span style="font-family:宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-family:calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">招生人数：</span>30<span style="font-family:宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family:;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family:;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-indent:14px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" class=" " border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中国特色社会主义理论与实践研究</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科学技术哲学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="3" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">金融经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">发展经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">能源经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级计量经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级宏观经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中级微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin:15px 0cm 0px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">国际贸易实务</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">政府管制与反垄断</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">现代商务策划与管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent:54px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><div align="center"><table style="margin:auto auto auto 36px;border:currentcolor;width:501px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm 7px;border:1px solid black;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">次</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">报名时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">开课时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">02020021</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2012</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">02020022</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【收费标准】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学费</span><span style="font-family:;">22000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元（刷卡、现金、支票均可），报名费</span><span style="font-family:;">200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元，教材资料费</span><span style="font-family:;">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">申请学位者参加硕士学位论文指导及答辩等费用，另按北京理工大学相关规定执行；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【证书颁发】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、学员修完全部课程，并通过结业考试后，经北京理工大学研究生院审核颁发结业证书。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、获得学士学位满三年，已通过所学专业课程的考核与国家组织的全国统一水平考试，并公开发表一篇相关论文，即可以进入硕士学位申请阶段。通过学校论文答辩与学位审批后，可以获得北京理工大学管理学硕士学位。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【特别提醒】</span><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;text-indent:35px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">交学校审核的所有证件材料等须是真实有效的，若因虚假材料造成一切后果由本人承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">申硕说明】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 32px;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">有关申请硕士学位事项按国务院学位委员会</span>[1998]54<span style="font-family:宋体;">号文件的规定和学校的相关规定执行。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">增值服务】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可免费参加北京理工大学管理与经济学院主办的五次高水平讲座；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可加入北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友会，拓宽人脉资源，参加丰富多彩的校友活动。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【联系方式】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名电话：</span>010-68918810&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;010-68918072&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18701396872</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名地点：北京理工大学（东门）管理与经济学院<span style="color:black;">主楼二层</span></span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span>224<span style="font-family:宋体;">室</span><span style="font-family:calibri;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">联</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">系</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">钟老师</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">李老师</span></span></p><p style="line-height:27px;"><span style="font-family:;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1354885159, 0);
INSERT INTO `np_courses` (`id`, `type`, `name`, `photo`, `professor`, `content`, `add_time`, `index`) VALUES
(39, '2', '2013年工商管理专业（企业管理方向）在职研究生课程进修班', '/upload/20130724/13746767723271.jpg', '', '<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: navy; font-family: ;"><img title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/13548868255274.png"/><img style="width: 291px; height: 58px;" title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/13548868254700.jpg" width="309" height="61"/>&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: navy; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color: navy; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班工商管理专业</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: navy; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 24px;">（企业管理方向）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color: navy; font-family: ;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: red; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">（可申请管理学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color: red; font-family: ;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 28px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，对接企业对人力资源工作岗位职业资格的需要，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family: ;">2013</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办工商管理专业（企业管理方向）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 102); font-family: 宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 102); font-family: ;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 21px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">1<span style="font-family: 宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 21px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">2<span style="font-family: 宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 21px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">3<span style="font-family: 宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 102); font-family: 宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 102); font-family: ;"></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">1<span style="font-family: 宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family: calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family: 宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family: 宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family: 宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family: 宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family: 宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family: 宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">2<span style="font-family: 宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family: 宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family: 宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 102); font-family: 宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 102); font-family: ;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 21px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">招生人数：</span>60<span style="font-family: 宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="color: navy; font-family: 宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color: navy; font-family: 宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color: navy; font-family: ;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 42px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family: ;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 42px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family: ;">/</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family: ;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 42px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: ;">6</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family: ;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 42px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family: ;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 102); font-family: 宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 102); font-family: ;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0px 28px; text-indent: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family: ;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 102); font-family: 宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 102); font-family: ;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 42px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 102); font-family: 宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 102); font-family: ;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin: auto auto auto 48px; border-collapse: collapse;" border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 89px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 499px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 89px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 247px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">中国特色社会主义理论与实践研究</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 252px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">自然辩证法概论</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 247px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 252px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 89px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="5" width="89"><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 247px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">现代管理理论与方法</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 252px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">战略管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 247px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">市场营销管理</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 252px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">财务管理理论与方法</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 247px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">宏观经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 252px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 247px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">人力资源管理</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 252px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">会计理论</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 247px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">品牌管理</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 252px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 89px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin: 15px 0cm 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 247px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">管理沟通</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 252px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">企业并购与公司治理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 247px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">员工关系管理</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0cm; width: 252px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">项目管理</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent: 54px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family: ;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="color: navy; font-family: 宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><strong><span style="color: navy; font-family: ;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin: auto auto auto 36px; border: currentColor; width: 501px; border-collapse: collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding: 0cm 7px; border: 1px solid black; width: 132px; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;">班</span></